&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;02:23:18.535  [TRACE] Npm.install dir=&#x2F;root&#x2F;.config&#x2F;opencode add=[@opencode-ai&#x2F;plugin@0.0.0-dev-xxx]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
